Note that because of approximations inherent in deriving equation \ref{eq:edotturb}, $\dot E_{\rm turb}$ is only  accurate to multiplicative factors of order unity (in contrast to $\dot E_{\rm cool}$,  $\dot E_{\rm SN}$, and $\dot E_{\rm out}$).

